Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人總是因某些事而迷茫 總是要不斷做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes of course…
